**MIXA-037 is complete.** Here's a summary of what was implemented:

## tRPC Layer (MIXA-037) - Done

### Architecture
- **Custom IPC transport** - No HTTP server needed. Uses `ipcMain.handle('trpc', ...)` in main process and `ipcRenderer.invoke('trpc', ...)` in preload, with a custom tRPC link in the renderer.

### Files Created
- `apps/desktop/src/main/trpc/trpc.ts` - tRPC instance with context type
- `apps/desktop/src/main/trpc/router.ts` - Root router merging 7 sub-routers
- `apps/desktop/src/main/trpc/ipc.ts` - IPC handler bridging Electron IPC to tRPC
- `apps/desktop/src/main/trpc/index.ts` - Exports
- **7 routers** in `routers/`:
  - `items.ts` - create, list, get, update, delete, search
  - `projects.ts` - create, list, get, update, delete
  - `tags.ts` - list, merge, rename
  - `search.ts` - hybrid search with filters (vector + FTS weights)
  - `chat.ts` - createConversation, sendMessage, listConversations, getConversation, deleteConversation
  - `settings.ts` - get, update (with default settings)
  - `engine.ts` - status, listModules, sendCommand
- `apps/desktop/src/renderer/trpc.ts` - tRPC client with custom IPC link

### Files Modified
- `apps/desktop/src/main/index.ts` - Calls `setupTRPCHandler()` on app ready
- `apps/desktop/src/preload/index.ts` - Exposes `trpc` method via contextBridge
- `apps/desktop/src/renderer/env.d.ts` - Extended ElectronAPI type
- `apps/desktop/tsconfig.web.json` - Updated rootDir for cross-process type imports

